(1135, '2010-09-30 00:01:18', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '', 2011, '    Our students will take the Major Field Test in Biology, prepared by Educational Testing Services (ETS). Additional information on the exam can be found at www.ets.org.', '    We will attempt to get all graduating seniors to take the exam.', 'Datatel reports that we have 18 BIO seniors, including both BA and BS', '    Several testing periods will be available early in Spring term 2011', '$26 per exam', '    Mean total score will be determined. Mean scores in each of four subfields established by ETS will also be determined. Additionally, nine assessment indicators are reported by ETS that report mean scores on more restricted topics. We hope to be able to identify subfields of Biology where our majors are particularly strong and those where they are particularly weak.', 'Bio Chair', '    We will compare current mean scores to national norms and historic data. Furthermore, we will compare scores in the four subfields to the Biology classes those students have taken and their performance in those classes. ', '    National comparative data will be available from ETS ', '', '2', '2'),
