er, the Biology department is in the midst of restructuring our curriculum.  New introductory courses will begin in the 2013-14 academic year and a new set of “sophomore core courses” will begin in the following year.  These data will provide crucial baseline data to help determine if our curricular changes affect students’ knowledge of the basic concepts and theories of biology.  ', '', '2', '2');
